’Ů@c590f3f6262185c24bca1bdaa78bd0b2d737a64f032818a0ae6e57eaaa3e0881ŮôTitle: title: math arctan
Path: Examples
Content:
Get the arctangent of 1
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 1 | math arctan
0.7853981633974483

```
Get the arctangent of -1 in degrees
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> -1 | math arctan --degrees
-45.0

```
